{
  "id": "adv_main_04_01_05",
  "title": "星空編1章5話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――三枝とどりきゅんの密会を見かけた翌日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day after Saegusa and DoriKyun’s secret meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 1.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_trouble-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.5666666508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（三枝さんは俺達に内緒でどりきゅんと会っていた……）\n（彼女達となんの話をしていたんだ？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Saegusa-san met DoriKyun secretly from us）\n（What did he talk about with them?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 9.2333333175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、眉間にしわが寄ってる……\nまた何か悩んでる……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san is frowning…\nAre you worried about something else?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.7613689433,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 15.0999999841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "もしかして、昨日の三枝さん達のことが\n気になってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perhaps‚ you're worried about what happened to\nSaegusa-san and the others yesterday?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2999999841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ……あんな光景を見たら、さすがにな\nあれから三枝さんとも連絡がつかないし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… after seeing that sight‚ I guess\nSince then‚ I haven't been able to contact Saegusa-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "夕べも、あの後すぐタクシーに乗って\nどこかに行っちゃいましたからね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Last night‚ he immediately got into a taxi\nand went somewhere",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 33.8666666508
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅんは……最近は目立った活動をしてなくて……\n解散するって噂もある……それと関係あるのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun… hasn't been very active recently…\nThere are also rumors of disbandment… It might be related to that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.4332246907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 43.3333333175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "解散の噂は俺も知っているが……もしかして事務所と\nうまくいっていないのか？　だとしたら三枝さんは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I also know about rumors of disbandment… but maybe things\naren't going well with the agency? If so‚ Saegusa-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 51.9333358606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ひょっとして、どりきゅんを星見プロに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe‚ he would send DoriKyun to Hoshimi Prods…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9333358606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 56.2333358606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "あり得る……\nもしそうなら、業界に激震が走る大ニュース……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could be…\nIf so‚ it would be big news for the industry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 62.3333358606
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いいか、ハッキリするまでこのことは他言無用だ\n絶対に誰にも言うんじゃないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Look‚ don't need to tell anyone about this until we know for sure\nNever tell anyone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 69.166669194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "わ、分かりました！　絶対に誰にも言いません！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay! I won't tell anyone!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.166669194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-szk004.m4a",
      "text": "ん、分かった。おくちチャック",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ok‚ I got it. I'll watch my mouth.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.4000025273,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2433.330806000001,
          "startTime": 75.8333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3133.3308060000036,
          "startTime": 76.5333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 76.366669194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様で～す！\nみんなで集まって、なんの話をしてるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your effort~!\nWhat are you all talking about when you're all gathered together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 82.7000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん！？\nべ、別に何も話してないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan!?\nW-We didn't really talk about anything!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4721739111,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "そう、なんでもない……\n隠し事なんて何もない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ it's nothing…\nThere's nothing to hide…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5600705207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 92.066669194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "隠し事？\nあ！　もしかして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hide?\nAh! Perhaps…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 96.9000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（まずいぞ、千紗と雫は隠し事に全く向いていない……）\n（これは、さすがにさくらも気付いたか？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（This is bad‚ Chisa and Shizuku are not at all suited to hiding something….）\n（Did Sakura know this fact?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4427612616,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_plan-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 106.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 107.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "さては……次のライブバトルの相手が決まったんですね\n誰なんですか？　私にも教えて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… I guess the opponent for the next live battle has been decided\nWho is it? Please let me know!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "（……さくらが天然気味で助かった）\n（そういえばトリエルの件も結論を出せていないな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…It was a good thing Sakura was a bit innocent）\n（Come to think of it‚ I still haven't come to a conclusion about TRINITYAiLE incident）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 121.2000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まだ決まっていないんだ。サニピと対戦を希望する\nグループはいるにはいるが、少し不安もあって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nothing has been decided yet. There are groups that want to match with Sunny Peace‚\nbut I'm a little worried about something…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.4870546818,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 128.266669194
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "不安？\nそれは、サニピが負けるかもしれないってことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Worry?\nIs it because Sunny Peace might lose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.0000025273,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sun-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 134.7000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-01-noon",
      "startTime": 134.7000025273
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05/sud_vo_adv_main_04_01_05-skr005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら大丈夫です！\nたとえ誰が相手でも、全力で戦って勝ってみせます！",
      "translations": {
